@node a_cosa_serve "Introduction"

        MiraFIND  works  with  AmigaGUIDE file  made  with
        MiraNAVIGATOR.
        This file  are archive  (in AmigaGUIDE format) for
        view and extract LHA, LZX, DMS and ZIP files.
        For a complete description of  these file read the
        documentation of MiraNAVIGATOR.
        MiraFIND examines the file and  search a string of
        characters then shows you in AmigaGUIDE format.
        MitraFIND works only with this kind of file.

