@node come_funziona "How does it work ?"

        At the start the program shows a simple interface.
        In  the  gadget  "String"  you  may  specify  the
        sequence of characters that you want to find.
        The quest  will do in  the file indicated  in the
        gadget "File" (This file must be created with the
        use of MiraNAVIGATOR).
        Use button "Search" to start the quest...
        After few  seconds the list of file that contents
        the string will  appear, now  you can extract  or
        view them.
        If something wrong read the @{"Installation" link installazione} chapter.

